Class CatalogObjectImpl

java.lang.Object
org.postgresql.pljava.pg.CatalogObjectImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
CatalogObject
Direct Known Subclasses:
CatalogObjectImpl.Addressed, TriggerImpl
public class CatalogObjectImpl extends Object implements CatalogObject
Implementation of the CatalogObject API for the PL/Java case of JVM running in the PostgreSQL backend process.
